text: Ilmir Fanilyevich Yakupov (; born 17 March 1994) is a Russian football player. He made his professional debut in the Russian Football National League for FC Sibir Novosibirsk on 11 July 2015 in a game against FC Volgar Astrakhan. ==References== ==External links== * Player page on the FNL website Category:1994 births Category:People from Ufimsky District Category:Living people Category:Russian footballers Category:FC Sibir Novosibirsk players Category:Association football forwards Category:FC Ufa players Category:FC Avangard Kursk players
